      "description": "sample -  - Determines whether record should sample the time slice or the current frame. You would generally want to use Current , for audio, as all frames will be evaluated.\t\nIf the interval is set to be the Current , it will always cook (only look at) the current frame (things downstream still cook regardless of this setting however). Thus, it should generally not be used for audio, but rather fro things like device input, because it interpolates the values between the captured frames.\n\n\n scur - sslice -",
